Note on data licensing:

Source data files in the `data/` directory (not stored in git) are produced by
third parties under their own terms:

  * U.S. Census Bureau (TIGER/Line, ACS, PL 94-171): public domain.
  * Minnesota Secretary of State precinct results: public record.
  * Minnesota Geospatial Commons "General Election Results by Precinct,
    2022-2030": open license (see dataset metadata).

When redistributing derived works, follow each source's attribution
requirements. Attribution notes are included in the rendered map footer and
in the report's Sources section.
